Title: Nonrelativistic Quantum Particle in a Curved Space as a Constrained
  System
Authors: A. Foerster, H. O. Girotti and P. S. Kuhn
Comments: 11 pages, latex, revtex, no figures. Accepted for publication in
  Phys. Lett. A
\\
  The operator and the functional formulations of the dynamics of constrained
systems are explored for determining unambiguously the quantum Hamiltonian of a
nonrelativistic particle in a curved space.
